channel.title: "Unexpected Server Response" or "Server must be down" errors
channel.description:
Hi, I tried to acces Moparscape using different servers (all online). Each time I logged in (Username Durial321 ; Pass is unknown to me, I hit my head on the keyboard lmao) i got 2 answers : the first one is "Unexpected server response, please use a different world" ; the last one is "Server must be down...". What's going on? Do I have to type real username and password? Are the servers ungoing an important update? Did I go something wrong with the loading?
I'll be grateful to whoever tells me how to access Moparscape.
PS : Yeah, I am fond of fake pictures...hence the name "durial321", greatest PKer of RuneScape II... :rolleyes:
-Aveyond06
